Rules and Configuration
No formal rules file or MCP server configuration was used. Claude was accessed through the standard claude.ai web interface. All prompts were written and refined iteratively by the student, with Claude used as a sounding board rather than a code generator.

What AI Did NOT Do

AI did not write the core application logic from scratch
AI did not design the database schema
AI did not build the core HTML, JavaScript, or Node.js structure
AI did not generate the resume preview or print layout logic
All code was written, reviewed, and understood by the student


Statement of Understanding
All code in this project, including any sections where AI provided assistance, has been reviewed and is understood by the student. 
